Our narrative is simple We cater to those who cherish the best of both worlds, offering an elegant escape from the ordinary all while allowing for the thrill of if you choose to stay late. Photos Weekly photos from Proper. Merch Proper Merch: TShirts & Hoodies. Contact Tune in and connect with Proper. Beyond ordinary bars, beyond conventional nightlife. Proper awaits, a meticulously crafted playground for the discerning. Dive into mid-century charm, savor meticulously crafted cocktails, and surrender to the hypnotic sway of curated music. We elevate the art of revelry, seamlessly blending hushed whispers with vibrant energy, crafting a late-night sanctuary unlike any other. Industry Night & DJ Speaker Giveaway Days Hours Minutes Seconds Weekly Event Timeless Brunch Proper, Orlando’s top spot for amazing cocktails and vinyl, is shaking things up with Timeless Brunch Sundays. This isn’t your average brunch; it’s a “grown and fun” party where you can kick back with incredible drinks and food that’s way Event Details » Proper Music Dive into sonic alchemy, where vinyl rules and local Selectors weave your next adventure in sound. Every night, our walls crackle with a curated all-genre symphony, from vintage soul whispers to pulse-pumping contemporary beats. This isn’t background noise, it’s your living room soundtrack, amplified. So raise a glass, let the needle drop, and let the music paint your night in vibrant rhythms. Find your groove, your tribe, your next favorite track – all spun with heart and soul, right here, right now. SOUND Selectors Forget generic sets and canned playlists. Immerse yourself in sonic alchemy with our handpicked Selectors, music magicians who conjure the perfect vibe every night. Live from our intimate stage, national acts unleash their raw energy, while homebodies catch the magic through our live streams. Whether you’re there or not, you’ll feel the electricity crackle. At Proper Orlando music reigns supreme weaving a tapestry of connection and genuine enjoyment that transcends social barriers. Step into a sanctuary for souls united by the universal language of melody and rhythm. SOUND System Transcend the typical bar soundscape. Immerse yourself in sonic nirvana with our Danley Sound flagship system, meticulously crafted by audio visionary Jeff Kenney. Soaring SH50 speakers, artfully positioned for uniform coverage, envelop the room in pristine fidelity and laser-sharp bass, guaranteeing aural bliss from whispered nuances to soaring crescendos. These are not mere speakers; they are auditory architects, meticulously sculpting soundscapes that dance around you. Fear not the potential for sonic booms – even at their peak, these audiophile marvels purr with exquisite control, thanks to their Class D power and ingenious design. These aren’t just speakers, they’re auditory architects. Each SH50 boasts unmatched precision and control, crafting soundscapes that dance around you. And don’t worry about ear-splitting blasts – even at their peak, they purr like audiophile kittens, thanks to the Class D power and clever design. Meet our Selectors, the maestros of ambiance. Throughout the day, they weave sonic spells with a curated repertoire and deft adjustments, transforming the atmosphere from hushed intimacy to room-filling immersion. It’s the difference between a hushed vinyl crackle and a symphony swirling around you. Let your ears wander into a sonic sanctuary. Make Reservations Note: Reservations will be at no cost before 9 PM. After 9 PM we charge a table-minimum or rate dependant on capacity and event. SMART Tech Step into a time capsule of mid-century modern style, where the warmth of vintage aesthetics meets the cutting-edge of sound technology. Our fully analog, high-fidelity system will transport you to a golden age of audio, while our user-friendly mobile app keeps you firmly anchored in the present. This intuitive app acts as your gateway to a world of sonic exploration. Seamlessly integrated with ChatGPT, WhatsApp, Shazam, Discogs, and Stripe, it unlocks a plethora of exciting features: Request your favorite tunes: Let our Selectors, the vinyl curators extraordinaire, know what tickles your ears. Show your appreciation: Interact and tip them in real-time, making their sonic sorcery even more rewarding. Tune in from anywhere: Witness their artistry live-streamed on Twitch, spreading the music magic beyond our walls. Shape our vinyl universe: Dive deep into our record library, suggest new additions, and even request albums for purchase – your taste truly matters. VIP vinyl collaboration: Elevate your experience as a VIP member by spinning your own selections, creating a shared musical tapestry. Be the maestro: As a guest or member, let your voice be heard. Suggest national acts you’d love to see perform live in our intimate space, and let us orchestrate the vinyl symphony. So, put your phone away, not to silence it, but to amplify your experience. At Proper, the past and present come together to create a symphony of sound, innovation, and community. Come, raise a glass, and let the music move you. James Zabiela At Proper Orlando Tue, April 29th | Limited Tickets! Skip to the content Home Menu Events Booking Reservations Photos Merch Contact Facebook Instagram James Zabiela April 29th, 2025 James Zabiela will be performing in Orlando at Proper on April 29th, 2025 ! Details * Only 100 Tickets will be sold * Early Bird: General Admission (SOLD OUT) Tier 1: General Admission (SOLD OUT) Tier 2: General Admission: (SOLD OUT) Tier 3: General Admission: $30 (Limited) Tier 4: General Admission: $35 (Limited) Tier 5: General Admission: $40 (Limited) tICKETS Get Tickets * Capacity Stricly Limited * * Only 100 Tickets will be sold * Share This Event Days Hours Minutes Seconds Tuesday, April 29th James Zabiela at Proper James Zabiela , born on August 7, 1979, in Southampton, England, is a highly respected DJ and producer in the electronic music scene. He initially gained recognition in 2000 by winning Muzik Magazine’s “Bedroom Bedlam” competition. This victory propelled him into the professional realm, leading to a signing with Sasha’s Excession DJ agency. Zabiela’s early signature sound was a blend of breakbeat and progressive house. Over time, his style has evolved to encompass progressive house, techno, and acid house, though elements of breakbeat often remain integral to his sets. He is celebrated for his exceptional turntable skills, creative use of loops and effects, and his mastery of Pioneer CDJ equipment, often incorporating Ableton Live and various controllers, including occasionally an iPad, into his performances. His technical prowess has earned him accolades as a “technical Jedi,” consistently pushing the boundaries of DJing. This expertise has even led to a long-standing relationship with Pioneer, where he provides feedback on their new DJ hardware. Throughout his career, Zabiela has released numerous mix albums and original tracks on esteemed labels such as Renaissance and his own imprint, Born Electric, established in 2012. Born Electric has showcased music from a diverse range of artists. James Zabiela’s dynamic and technically intricate DJ sets have captivated audiences worldwide, establishing him as a prominent figure in electronic music.
